 TDS File Format
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

TDS File Format

* File Header

*---------------------+------------------------------------------------------+
| <<Type>>            | <<Description>>
*---------------------+------------------------------------------------------+
| char[3] header      | The file header. Must be "TDS".
*---------------------+------------------------------------------------------+
| byte version        | The file version. Must be 1.
*---------------------+------------------------------------------------------+
| byte flags          | File Flags.
|                     | Bit 0: File endianess (0=Little Endian, 1=Big Endian)
*---------------------+------------------------------------------------------+
| int chunks          | The number of chunks following the header
*---------------------+------------------------------------------------------+


* Model Chunk

*---------------------+------------------------------------------------------+
| <<Type>>            | <<Description>>
*---------------------+------------------------------------------------------+
| char[3] header      | The file header. Must be "TDM".
*---------------------+------------------------------------------------------+

